\chapter{Modules \& functions}
\label{\detokenize{index:module-main}}\label{\detokenize{index:modules-functions}}\index{module@\spxentry{module}!main@\spxentry{main}}\index{main@\spxentry{main}!module@\spxentry{module}}

\section{main.py}
\label{\detokenize{index:main-py}}\begin{quote}\begin{description}
\item[{author}] \leavevmode
Olli\sphinxhyphen{}Pekka Tikkanen

\item[{synopsis}] \leavevmode
This is the main program to run the model

\end{description}\end{quote}

The purpose of this main file is to provide an easy way to run the model.
All the model parameters are set in the file and are taken from \sphinxhref{https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00468-005-0014-6}{Hölttä et. al. 2006}
or \sphinxhref{https://academic.oup.com/aob/article/114/4/653/2769025}{Nikinmaa et. al., (2014)}.

A sine\sphinxhyphen{}like behaviour is assumed for the transpiration and photosynthesis

\sphinxhref{transpiration\_rate.png}{\sphinxincludegraphics{{transpiration_rate}.png}}
